{"tid":1832133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"得個chem degree，我入唔入到香港工程師學會登記做功能組別？","createTime":"2020-01-21T02:55:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-01T16:11:08.000Z","uid":274732,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0499fa365294987cbe24ad388c2f131bcaba04eb","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:55:19.000Z","msg":"睇完燒山講<br />\n佢話只要你係ad hd degree都可以登記<br />\n但睇HKIE website要比會費<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xzfXgwU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxzfXgwU.png&h=ce93b229&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊個類別先有權投票而又比最小錢申請？<br />\n<br />\n我於是再睇下wiki<br />\nWiki所指&rdquo;投票&rdquo;係內部投票定功能組別投票呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AkOeiL9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAkOeiL9.png&h=f10d4ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇會員解答下<br />\n每年咁多bsc畢業<br />\n可以登記投票就好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee88fc09168f3ab7c039999b7299852c325b1bdf","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:56:18.000Z","msg":"推1<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eefed1d514e6f13aab4b8e2186d5781999c7f04","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:57:21.000Z","msg":"以下為香港工程師學會的21個專業界別[21]：<br />\n<br />\n航空界別（Aircraft Discipline）<br />\n生物醫學界別（Biomedical Discipline）<br />\n建造界別（Building Discipline）<br />\n屋宇裝備界別（Building Services Discipline）<br />\n化工界別（Chemical Discipline）<br />\n土木界別（Civil Discipline）<br />\n控制、自動化及儀器儀表界別（Control, Automation &amp; Instrumentation Discipline）<br />\n電機界別（Electrical Discipline）<br />\n電子界別（Electronics Discipline）<br />\n環境界別（Environmental Discipline）<br />\n能源界別（Energy Discipline）<br />\n消防界別（Fire Discipline）<br />\n燃氣界別（Gas Discipline）<br />\n岩土界別（Geotechnical Discipline）<br />\n資訊科技界別（Information Technology Discipline）<br />\n物流及運輸界別（Logistics &amp; Transportation Discipline）<br />\n製造及工業界別（Manufacturing &amp; Industrial Discipline）<br />\n輪機及造船界別（Marine &amp; Naval Architecture）<br />\n材料界別（Materials Discipline）<br />\n機械界別（Mechanical Discipline）<br />\n結構界別（Structural Discipline）"},{"pid":"71ddc21e7a40a7b195efb2700d094274065e4140","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T02:58:10.000Z","msg":"推2<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"122151a8a72212b6dc79cfe76ce4032b593792d2","tid":1832133,"uid":7849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"好可惜要charter左先有投票權"},{"pid":"aa47590c2bce96eae7130cb0020399df8d24cfc2","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122151a8a72212b6dc79cfe76ce4032b593792d2","tid":1832133,"uid":7849,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:02:25.000Z","msg":"好可惜要charter左先有投票權"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:03:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又係圈內小圈子"},{"pid":"ea4710c07bccc0da1e9bba8897fcd14b8facc460","tid":1832133,"uid":276273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:11:11.000Z","msg":"有無member推薦?<br />\n當年嘗試申請Associate，要揾member推薦，揾到阿Sir推薦，<br />\n最後因為主業係Telecom， 申請失敗"},{"pid":"0a60d22ca6c5d0cfefb4f6f024e98c319622dad5","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"推3<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n工程學會巴打幫唔幫到手"},{"pid":"fb0dd2914fec50efb1fae5f2d53eff564838e07d","tid":1832133,"uid":171668,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:35:12.000Z","msg":"香港工程師學會係小圈子中既小圈子"},{"pid":"a377b7213f443611bad41b010d687e8874affe39","tid":1832133,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor